title: Jeff Beck & Tal Wilkenfeld (Complete Concert w/info) 2007
description:
I wanted to put this up in complete form because it deserves justice.

Jeff Beck-Guitars

Tal Wilkenfeld-Bass

Jason Rebello-Keyboards

Vinnie Colaiuta-Drums

From the Crossroads 2007 Concert in Chicago.

Setlist (in order)

Resolution
Eternity's Breath
You Never Know
'Cause We've Ended As Lovers
Stratus
Behind The Veil/Nadia
Led Boots
Angel (footsteps)
Big Block

Encore:
Good Bye Pork Pie Hat/Brush With The Blues
A Day In The Life

Important-I've added an extra version of Big Block which is better in clarity 
but is a different camera angle. Also included are alternitive preformances
of Pork Pie Hat and Blue Wind from earlier concerts. Big Block in the main folder
is poor quality video but has a better take on the performance by the band. (IMHO)

Information and photos-wallpapers included in download. 
Due to the source, the quality is good but in no way perfect.
For more information go to www.whereseric.com and look up the show.
